  "title": "test: update guidelines and clean up tests",
  "body": "This is a followup of the work we've done with @dhayab in #5674.\r\n\r\n- Slightly updates the README in the common test suite\r\n- Removes leftover tests for breadcrumb we no longer needed\r\n- Puts more tests in common for breadcrumb\r\n\r\nWe can probably start migrating many tests to the common test suites and remove a lot of other tests. This will make the inconsistencies stand out and we can start better testing our widgets and plan for changes in future majors.",
